00:23:49.210 --> 00:23:51.255
but to live in the future.

359
00:23:51.430 --> 00:23:54.215
everyone will need
a fully functioning brain.

360
00:23:54.389 --> 00:24:01.483
Everyone will need to be able
to think clearly.
straightforwardly in mono.

